### 10.2 输入命令定义

```csharp
public sealed record MoveCommand(int Frame, long ActorId, float X, float Y);
public sealed record SkillCommand(int Frame, long ActorId, int SkillSlot, float TargetX, float TargetY);
public sealed record StopCommand(int Frame, long ActorId);
