## 十四、SubFeature 模式规范

### 14.1 SubFeature 设计原则

**SubFeature 是模块化的功能扩展组件，用于分离战斗会话的不同职责。**

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Session SubFeature 架构图 │
│ │
│ ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ ETBattleComponent │ │
│ │ (生命周期管理) │ │
│ └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
│ │ │
│ ├── ETSessionEventsSubFeature (事件系统) - 必须首先创建 │
│ ├── ETSessionPlanSubFeature (计划) │
│ ├── ETSessionLifecycleSubFeature (生命周期) │
│ ├── ETSessionSnapshotRoutingSubFeature (快照路由) │
│ ├── ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature (帧循环) │
│ └── ETSessionReplaySubFeature (回放录制) │
│ │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### 14.2 SubFeature 接口定义

```csharp
/// <summary>
/// Session SubFeature 基接口
/// 所有 SubFeature 必须实现此接口
/// </summary>
public interface ISessionSubFeature
{
    /// <summary>
    /// 附加到战斗组件时调用
    /// </summary>
    void OnAttach(ETBattleComponent battle);

    /// <summary>
    /// 从战斗组件分离时调用
    /// </summary>
    void OnDetach(ETBattleComponent battle);

    /// <summary>
    /// 会话运行时每帧调用
    /// </summary>
    void Tick(ETBattleComponent battle, float deltaTime);
}
```

### 14.3 SubFeature Component 规范

**Component 只存储数据，System 处理逻辑：**

```csharp
// ✅ 正确：SubFeature Component 只定义数据
[ComponentOf(typeof(Scene))]
public class ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature : Entity, IAwake, IDestroy
{
    /// <summary>
    /// Owner battle component reference
    /// </summary>
    public ETBattleComponent Owner { get; set; }

    /// <summary>
    /// Tick rate (frames per second)
    /// </summary>
    public int TickRate { get; set; }

    /// <summary>
    /// Is the tick loop running
    /// </summary>
    public bool IsRunning { get; set; }

    public void Awake()
    {
        TickRate = 30;
        IsRunning = false;
    }

    public void Destroy()
    {
        Owner = null;
    }
}

// ❌ 错误：SubFeature Component 包含业务逻辑
[ComponentOf(typeof(Scene))]
public class ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature : Entity, IAwake
{
    public ETBattleComponent Owner { get; set; }

    public void Awake()
    {
        // ❌ 不应在 Awake 中执行初始化逻辑
        Log.Info("Starting tick loop...");
        StartLoop();
    }

    private void StartLoop() // ❌ 逻辑应该在 System 中
    {
        // ...
    }
}
```

### 14.4 SubFeature System 规范

```csharp
// ✅ 正确：SubFeature System 使用 partial class + 扩展方法
[EntitySystemOf(typeof(ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature))]
[FriendOf(typeof(ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature))]
[FriendOf(typeof(ETBattleSessionHooks))]
public static partial class ETSessionTickLoopSubFeatureSystem
{
    [EntitySystem]
    private static void Awake(this ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature self)
    {
        Log.Info("[TickLoop] System awake");
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// Attach to battle component
    /// </summary>
    public static void OnAttach(this ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature self, ETBattleComponent battle)
    {
        self.Owner = battle;
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// Start tick loop
    /// </summary>
    public static void Start(this ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature self)
    {
        self.IsRunning = true;
        Log.Info("[TickLoop] Tick loop started");
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// Stop tick loop
    /// </summary>
    public static void Stop(this ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature self)
    {
        self.IsRunning = false;
        Log.Info("[TickLoop] Tick loop stopped");
    }
}
```

### 14.5 SubFeature 创建顺序

SubFeature 必须按依赖顺序创建：

```csharp
// 在 ETBattleComponentSystem.InitializeBattle 中：
public static void InitializeBattle(this ETBattleComponent self, BattleStartPlan plan, ITextAssetLoader textAssetLoader)
{
    // 1. EventsSubFeature 必须首先创建（其他 SubFeature 依赖它）
    var eventsSubFeature = scene.AddComponent<ETSessionEventsSubFeature>();
    eventsSubFeature.OnAttach(self);

    // 2. PlanSubFeature
    var planSubFeature = scene.AddComponent<ETSessionPlanSubFeature>();
    planSubFeature.OnAttach(self);

    // 3. LifecycleSubFeature
    var lifecycleSubFeature = scene.AddComponent<ETSessionLifecycleSubFeature>();
    lifecycleSubFeature.OnAttach(self);

    // 4. SnapshotRoutingSubFeature
    var snapshotRoutingSubFeature = scene.AddComponent<ETSessionSnapshotRoutingSubFeature>();
    snapshotRoutingSubFeature.OnAttach(self);

    // 5. TickLoopSubFeature
    var tickLoopSubFeature = scene.AddComponent<ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature>();
    tickLoopSubFeature.OnAttach(self);

    // 6. ReplaySubFeature
    var replaySubFeature = scene.AddComponent<ETSessionReplaySubFeature>();
    replaySubFeature.OnAttach(self);
}
```

### 14.6 SubFeature 禁止事项

| 禁止 | 说明 | 正确做法 |
|------|------|----------|
| ❌ SubFeature 直接修改其他 SubFeature 状态 | 通过 Hooks 或生命周期方法通信 | 使用 `OnAttach`/`OnDetach`/`Tick` 接口 |
| ❌ SubFeature 在构造函数中执行逻辑 | Component 只存储数据 | 在 `Awake` 或 `OnAttach` 中设置默认值 |
| ❌ 跨 SubFeature 直接调用方法 | 破坏模块化 | 通过 Hooks 订阅/发布事件 |

## 十五、Hooks 系统规范

### 15.1 Hooks 设计原则

**ETBattleSessionHooks 提供事件钩子，用于 SubFeature 之间的松耦合通信。**

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Hooks 系统架构图 │
│ │
│ ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ ETBattleSessionHooks │ │
│ │ │ │
│ │ Action OnPreTick; // 每帧前调用 │ │
│ │ Action OnPostTick; // 每帧后调用 │ │
│ │ Action OnFirstFrameReceived; // 首帧收到时调用 │ │
│ │ Action OnSessionStarted; // 会话开始时调用 │ │
│ │ Action OnSessionFailed; // 会话失败时调用 │ │
│ │ Action OnSessionStarting; // 会话即将开始时调用 │ │
│ │ Action OnSessionStopping; // 会话即将停止时调用 │ │
│ └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
│ │ │
│ │ 订阅 │ │
│ ├── SubFeature A ──▶ OnPreTick ──▶ 执行前置逻辑 │ │
│ ├── SubFeature B ──▶ OnPostTick ──▶ 执行后置逻辑 │ │
│ └── ETBattleComponent ──▶ OnSessionStarting ──▶ 启动 TickLoop │ │
│ │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### 15.2 Hooks Component 定义

```csharp
[ComponentOf(typeof(Scene))]
public class ETBattleSessionHooks : Entity, IAwake, IDestroy
{
    // ============== Session Lifecycle Hooks ==============

    /// <summary>
    /// Called before each tick
    /// </summary>
    public Action<float> OnPreTick { get; set; }

    /// <summary>
    /// Called after each tick
    /// </summary>
    public Action<float> OnPostTick { get; set; }

    /// <summary>
    /// Called when first frame is received
    /// </summary>
    public Action OnFirstFrameReceived { get; set; }

    /// <summary>
    /// Called when session starts
    /// </summary>
    public Action<BattleStartPlan> OnSessionStarted { get; set; }

    /// <summary>
    /// Called when session fails
    /// </summary>
    public Action<Exception> OnSessionFailed { get; set; }

    /// <summary>
    /// Called when session is about to start
    /// </summary>
    public Action OnSessionStarting { get; set; }

    /// <summary>
    /// Called when session is stopping
    /// </summary>
    public Action OnSessionStopping { get; set; }

    public void Awake() { }

    public void Destroy()
    {
        // 清理所有 Action
        OnPreTick = null;
        OnPostTick = null;
        OnFirstFrameReceived = null;
        OnSessionStarted = null;
        OnSessionFailed = null;
        OnSessionStarting = null;
        OnSessionStopping = null;
    }
}
```

### 15.3 Hooks 调用方法

```csharp
public static partial class ETBattleSessionHooksSystem
{
    /// <summary>
    /// Invoke session starting hook
    /// </summary>
