### 15.4 订阅 Hooks 示例

```csharp
// ✅ 正确：在 System 中订阅 Hooks
[EntitySystemOf(typeof(ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature))]
[FriendOf(typeof(ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature))]
[FriendOf(typeof(ETBattleSessionHooks))]
public static partial class ETSessionTickLoopSubFeatureSystem
{
    /// <summary>
    /// Subscribe to hooks
    /// </summary>
    public static void SubscribeToHooks(ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature self)
    {
        var scene = self.Scene();
        var hooks = scene?.GetComponent<ETBattleSessionHooks>();
        if (hooks == null)
            return;

        hooks.OnPreTick += (deltaTime) => OnPreTickHook(self, deltaTime);
        hooks.OnPostTick += (deltaTime) => OnPostTickHook(self, deltaTime);
    }

    private static void OnPreTickHook(ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature self, float deltaTime)
    {
        // 前置 Tick 逻辑
    }

    private static void OnPostTickHook(ETSessionTickLoopSubFeature self, float deltaTime)
    {
        // 后置 Tick 逻辑
    }
}
```

### 15.5 Hooks 禁止事项

| 禁止 | 说明 | 正确做法 |
|------|------|----------|
| ❌ 在 Component 构造函数中订阅 Hooks | Component 只存储数据 | 在 `OnAttach` 或专门初始化方法中订阅 |
| ❌ 持有 Hooks 强引用导致内存泄漏 | 应在 `OnDetach` 中取消订阅 | 在 `Destroy` 中清理 `Action = null` |
| ❌ Hooks 中执行耗时操作 | 可能阻塞帧 | 只执行轻量级逻辑 |

## 十六、Driver Bridge 模式规范

### 16.1 Driver Bridge 设计原则

**ETBattleDriverBridge 封装与 BattleDriver 的交互逻辑，提供统一的访问接口。**

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Driver Bridge 架构图 │
│ │
│ ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ ETBattleComponent │ │
│ │ │ │
│ │ - BattleDriver (ETMobaBattleDriver) │ │
│ └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
│ │ │
│ ▼ │
│ ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ ETBattleDriverBridge (静态辅助类) │ │
│ │ │ │
│ │ + SubmitMoveInput(ETBattleComponent, actorId, x, y) │ │
│ │ + SubmitSkillInput(ETBattleComponent, actorId, slot, x, y) │ │
│ │ + ProcessInput(ETBattleComponent, currentFrame) │ │
│ │ + GetWorld(ETBattleComponent): IWorld │ │
│ │ + TryResolve<T>(ETBattleComponent, out T): bool │ │
│ └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
│ │ │
│ ▼ │
│ ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ ETMobaBattleDriver (Component) │ │
│ │ │ │
│ │ - IWorldManager WorldManager │ │
│ │ - HostRuntime HostRuntime │ │
│ │ - FrameSnapshotDispatcher SnapshotDispatcher │ │
│ │ - ... │ │
│ └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### 16.2 Driver Bridge 模板

```csharp
/// <summary>
/// Battle driver bridge
/// Encapsulates interaction logic with BattleDriver
/// All methods delegate to ETMobaBattleDriverSystem extension methods
/// </summary>
public static class ETBattleDriverBridge
{
    /// <summary>
    /// Submit move input
    /// </summary>
    public static void SubmitMoveInput(ETBattleComponent self, long actorId, float targetX, float targetZ)
    {
        if (self.BattleDriver is ETMobaBattleDriver driver)
        {
            ETMobaBattleDriverSystem.SubmitMoveInput(driver, (int)actorId, targetX, targetZ);
        }
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// Submit skill input
    /// </summary>
    public static void SubmitSkillInput(ETBattleComponent self, long actorId, int slot, float targetX, float targetZ)
    {
        if (self.BattleDriver is ETMobaBattleDriver driver)
        {
            ETMobaBattleDriverSystem.SubmitSkillInput(driver, (int)actorId, slot, targetX, targetZ);
        }
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// Get World
    /// </summary>
    public static IWorld GetWorld(ETBattleComponent self)
    {
        if (self.BattleDriver is ETMobaBattleDriver driver)
        {
            return driver.World;
        }
        return null;
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// Try resolve service from moba.core
    /// </summary>
    public static bool TryResolve<T>(ETBattleComponent self, out T service) where T : class
    {
        service = null;
        if (self.BattleDriver is ETMobaBattleDriver driver)
        {
            return ETMobaBattleDriverSystem.TryResolve(driver, out service);
        }
        return false;
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// Start battle driver
    /// </summary>
    public static void Start(ETBattleComponent self)
    {
        if (self.BattleDriver is ETMobaBattleDriver driver)
        {
            ETMobaBattleDriverSystem.StartBattle(driver);
        }
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// Stop battle driver
    /// </summary>
    public static void Stop(ETBattleComponent self)
    {
        if (self.BattleDriver is ETMobaBattleDriver driver)
        {
            ETMobaBattleDriverSystem.StopBattle(driver);
        }
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// Get current frame number
    /// </summary>
    public static int GetCurrentFrame(ETBattleComponent self)
    {
        if (self.BattleDriver is ETMobaBattleDriver driver)
        {
            return driver.CurrentFrame;
        }
        return 0;
    }
}
```

### 16.3 Driver Bridge 禁止事项

| 禁止 | 说明 | 正确做法 |
|------|------|----------|
| ❌ 在 BattleDriver 中直接实现业务逻辑 | 应委托给 System | 在 `ETMobaBattleDriverSystem` 中实现 |
| ❌ 绕过 Bridge 直接访问 Driver | Bridge 提供统一接口 | 使用 `ETBattleDriverBridge.TryResolve<T>()` |
| ❌ 在 Bridge 中缓存引用 | 可能导致引用失效 | 每次通过 `self.BattleDriver` 获取 |

## 十七、ETUnit 子组件模式规范

### 17.1 子组件设计原则

**ETUnit 作为根实体持有子组件，通过子组件 ID 管理子组件生命周期。**

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ ETUnit 子组件架构图 │
│ │
│ ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ ETUnit (根实体) │ │
│ │ │ │
│ │ - Id: ET 框架自动生成 │ │
│ │ - MetaId: 子组件 ID │ │
│ │ - TransformId: 子组件 ID │ │
│ │ - CharacterId: 子组件 ID │ │
│ │ - SkillListId: 子组件 ID │ │
│ │ - BuffListId: 子组件 ID │ │
│ │ │ │
│ │ 通过 GetChild<T>(id) 获取子组件 │ │
│ └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
│ │ │
│ ├── ETUnitMetaComponent (元数据) │
│ ├── ETUnitTransformComponent (变换) │
